title: SJ - Swedish Railways
description: SJ express trains with buffet cars offer a vegan breakfast and vegan hot lunch/dinner. The breakfast consists of bread, vegan cheese, a tomato, yoghurt, apple juice, and coffee, tea, or hot chocolate. The lunch/dinner consists of a hot meal that changes each day plus a soft drink and hot drink of choice. Vegan meals are also gluten-free. To guarantee availability, these can be pre-ordered up to 24 hours prior to departure, either when booking tickets online, calling, or at any SJ travel office.
